<h1>Assisted Living</h1>  <hr /> <p>As you transition into new stages of life, BaneCare&rsquo;s assisted living residences offer a full-service, social lifestyle for those who are looking to remain independent with increased convenience, activity and companionship. Our assisted living residence offer complete housekeeping services, dining services, activities and social happenings, as well as health and transportation services for our residents.&nbsp;</p>  <p>At BaneCare, our Assisted Living services ensure that your needs are always met. You will never have to worry about preparing a meal ever again, as our exemplary chefs and culinary staff provides delicious, healthy breakfast, lunch and dinner every single day for our residents.</p>  <p>Our licensed, compassionate staff offers the support that our residents need to live life to the fullest, and with the peace of mind that their basic needs are taken care of. It is about enjoyment, fulfillment and loving life! A full list of services follows:</p>  <ul style="margin-left: 40px;"> 	<li>Choice of private and semi-private apartments</li> 	<li>Assistance with activities of daily living</li> 	<li>Gourmet resident-style dining</li> 	<li>Scheduled transportation to appointments, religious services, shopping and cultural events</li> 	<li>Housekeeping and linen service</li> 	<li>Social, recreational, educational and spiritual activities</li> 	<li>Medication monitoring</li> 	<li>Wellness programs</li> 	<li>Outings to concerts, museums and the theater</li> </ul>  <h3><span style="color:#3399cc"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif"><em>For more information, please visit our Assisted Living pages:</em></span></span></h3>  <hr /> <div class="btgrid"> <div class="row row-1"> <div class="col col-md-4"> <div class="content"> <p><br /> <a href="/Hancock-Park-Assisted-Living-Residence"><img alt="" class="shadow" src="/apps/_ee/files/hancockpark-ext.jpg" style="width:100%" /><br /> <br /> Hancock Park Assisted Living